ygData.messageBody:
Sorry to hear that Foleen, I have actually been
playing like crazy lately, love the new BL class. My BL
name is Caracas, if ye still have the account active
and need to unload some gear so that it does not go
to waste please send me an e-mail. BTW What game are
you thinking about venturing into next? Do you have
diablo II? I have it but am a noobie, just got past
chapter one with all my chars (have 1 for each class) so
shoot me an e-mail if you play that as well. Take care
and good luck!<br><br>Jonquil<br>Lvl 45 Wizzy on
E'ci<br>Caracas<br>Lvl 31 BL on E'ci
